# DeepSeek-Local

ğŸš€ **DeepSeek-Local** is a Python package that allows you to run **DeepSeek-Coder** locally using **Ollama**. With this package, you can generate and modify code using **DeepSeek-Coder**, all without requiring an internet connection!

---

## âœ¨ Features
- **Offline AI Coding Assistance** â€“ Run DeepSeek-Coder locally via Ollama.
- **Simple Installation** â€“ Easy setup with `pip install`.
- **Seamless Integration** â€“ Use the package in any Python project.
- **No Internet Required** â€“ Works entirely on your local machine.

